<item>
            <title>[LU-9060] e2fsprogs support of project qutoas</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9060</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Looks like &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4017&quot; title=&quot;Add project quota support feature&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4017&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4017&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; project quotas will be part of 2.10 master branch.&lt;br/&gt;
What is status of userspace tools ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I see there has been patched fo lfs &amp;amp; lctl. &lt;br/&gt;
Do e2fsprogs need updating ?&lt;br/&gt;
Is there roadmap/timeline to update e2fsprogs to support project quotas ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;thanks&lt;/p&gt;</description>
